1. Application build on Javascript frameworks angular 6 and for fronend component ionic has used latest version
2. As mention in task its created for demo of skills 
3. User can find the list of courses on tap user can read the details of the courses.
4. It displays the total number of Courses found
5. Displays the total number of Courses found
6. User is able to sort based on Next Session Date and Length


Running environment
1. Download the repositorie and  do npm install on root of repositorie
2. Install latest ionic frameworks for components
3. do ionic serve

